  <p>
    AIWA-Michigan is a group of Detroit-area South Asian Women who seek to
    promote awareness of issues relevant to ourselves and our community.
    Through seminars and activities we are increasing the knowledge of health,
    financial, and retirement planning in our community. We also provide
